    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国议员支持他信女儿出任下一任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-loyalist-emerges-pm-frontrunner-as-parties-begin-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦的女儿目前最有可能成为这个东南亚国家的下一任总理，这一举动标志着在周三另一名党员被赶下台后，泰国政府的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-loyalist-emerges-pm-frontrunner-as-parties-begin-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新泽西州州长墨菲将任命前助理接替梅内德斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/new-jersey-s-murphy-to-appoint-former-aide-to-replace-menendez</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士周三晚间透露，新泽西州州长菲尔墨菲将任命其前幕僚长接替上个月因联邦腐败指控被定罪的参议员鲍勃梅嫩德斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/new-jersey-s-murphy-to-appoint-former-aide-to-replace-menendez</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡下一任总统竞选的关键候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/the-key-contenders-in-race-to-become-sri-lanka-s-next-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡下个月举行的总统选举正成为政治精英与曾因武装叛乱而臭名昭著的左翼组织之间的战场，候选人争夺负责监督亟待改革的经济的最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/the-key-contenders-in-race-to-become-sri-lanka-s-next-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
